key_privacy_intro: We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of data we collect, the purposes for which we use it, and the safeguards we implement to ensure its security.
key_data_collection: We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, as well as technical data including IP address, browser type, device information, and cookies, when you interact with our services.
key_cookie_usage: We utilize cookies and similar tracking technologies to understand user behavior, enhance user experience, and improve the performance and security of our website. Additionally, we may integrate third-party analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics, Hotjar) to support these functions.
key_data_usage: The data collected is used to operate and improve our services, tailor content and features to user preferences, analyze traffic patterns, ensure platform security, and notify users of relevant updates or changes.
key_user_control: You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings. You may also opt out of third-party data collection using tools provided by external providers.
key_data_protection: We implement industry-standard technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, modification, disclosure, or destruction.
key_data_sharing: We do not share your personal data with third parties without your explicit consent, except when required by law or necessary for service delivery (e.g., hosting or analytics providers).
key_policy_changes: We reserve the right to amend this Privacy Policy at any time. Updates will be posted on this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any changes.
